     task(subagent_type="oracle", run_in_background=true, load_skills=[], prompt="<filesystem boundary>\n\nYou are a brutally honest technical reviewer. Review this embedded plan for logical gaps, unstated assumptions, sequencing mistakes, missing dependencies, missing edge cases, and overcomplexity. Also inspect these referenced repo files directly: <list>. THE PLAN:\n<embedded plan content>")
     ```

If the user passed `--xhigh`, tell Oracle to be exhaustive.

4. Save or update `.context/codex-oracle-session-id` with the returned Oracle session identifier or your own stable thread key for follow-ups.

5. Present the full streamed output:

```
ORACLE SAYS (consult):
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
<full output, verbatim>
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
